name: The RA! Awards x 2022 NFTs of the Year

metadata.name: The RA! Awards x 2022 NFTs of the Year Poster
metadata.description:
The RA! Awards is an Internet-first awards ceremony for the best NFTs of the year according to the fans, not price.

This commemorative poster was created for the second annual RA! Awards - the first ever RA! Awards held completely on-chain using RARA's social curation protocol.

Read more about about [The RA! Awards x 2022 NFTs of the Year](https://rara.mirror.xyz/TlmcyAV2ixHYYik8Elhpix3iZjHCGeOcjJoyxfyHw3Q).

To learn more about RARA, go to [RARA.social](http://rara.social/).
